Insider Activity


Individual




Paul D. Arling



Mr. Paul D. Arling is Independent Director at Milestone AV Technologies, Inc. and Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Universal Electronics, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Milestone AV Technologies, Inc. 
Mr. Arling was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer by LESCO, Inc., Planning Director by Imperial Wallcoverings, and Executive Vice President by Michael Allen Co. 
He received his undergraduate degree from The Wharton School of the University of Pennsylvania and an MBA from The Wharton School of the University of Pennsylvania. 



